---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting to Puerto Jimenez | Travel Guide">
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Getting to Puerto Jimenez</h1>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">By Plane</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    The fastest and most convenient way to reach Puerto Jimenez is by small aircraft.
                    Several domestic airlines operate daily flights from San José.
                </p>
                <!-- Flight details to be added -->
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">By Bus</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">From San José Airport</h3>
                    <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Take a TUASA bus to San José (approximately $6)
                            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2">
                                <li>Bus stop is located right outside the airport</li>
                                <li>Journey time: approximately 30-45 minutes</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        
                        <li>Once at TUASA terminal, you have two options:
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-md mt-2">
                                <h4 class="font-medium">Option 1 - Direct Route:</h4>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                                    <li>Take a taxi to Caribbean Bus Terminal (approximately $10)</li>
                                    <li>Take Transportes Blanco bus directly to Puerto Jiménez</li>
                                    <li>Departure time: 12:00 PM</li>
                                    <li>Cost: approximately $17</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-md mt-2">
                                <h4 class="font-medium">Option 2 - Via Golfito:</h4>
                                <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                                    <li>Take a taxi to Tracopa Bus Terminal ($12)</li>
                                    <li>Take a bus to either Golfito or Rio Claro ($17)</li>
                                    <li>Routes available:
                                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                                            <li>Coastal Route (Ruta Costanera)</li>
                                            <li>Mountain Route (Ruta Cerro)</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>

                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-md">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Final Leg - Ferry Service</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
                            <li>From Rio Claro, take a bus to Golfito Ferry Terminal ($3)</li>
                            <li>Take the ferry to Puerto Jiménez ($14)</li>
                            <li>Multiple departures daily (limited capacity)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Important Maps</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/HpHUj2pKGpr5RTVs5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                   class="block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="font-medium">Coastal Route Map</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">View the coastal route from San José to Rio Claro</p>
                </a>
                
                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/xjzS5QsACZVSCTa58" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
                   class="block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                    <h3 class="font-medium">Rio Claro to Golfito Route</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">View the route from Rio Claro to Golfito Ferry Terminal</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
